{
  "text": "Second, we build on the relatively scarce literature on the post-entry performance of INVs by attempting to understand the capabilities and underlying resources and strategies, which may explain the post-entry performance of these rapidly internationalising firms (e.g., Cavusgil and [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Our study contributes to the literature on the determinants of the postentry performance of INVs by simultaneously considering the roles of the firms' resources, business strategies and capabilities on their company performance, which has received less attention in the literature (e.g., [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] .",
